com.apple.eawt.event

Packages that use com.apple.eawt.event
com.apple.eawt.event Classes for receiving gesture events. 
 

Classes in com.apple.eawt.event used by com.apple.eawt.event
GestureEvent
          Abstract event all gestures inherit from.
GestureListener
          Marker interface for all gesture sub-types.
GesturePhaseEvent
          Event indicating the user has started or stopped a continuous gesture.
GesturePhaseListener
          Listener interface for receiving notification that a continuous gesture (like rotate or scale) has started or stopped.
MagnificationEvent
          Event encapsulating a relative magnification scale performed by the user.
MagnificationListener
          Listener interface for receiving magnification events.
RotationEvent
          Event encapsulating a relative rotation performed by the user.
RotationListener
          Listener interface for receiving rotation events.
SwipeEvent
          Event indicating a swipe was performed by the user.
SwipeListener
          Listener interface for receiving swipe events.
